{
  "name": "RPlog_The_Making_of_an_apprentice",
  "title": "The Making of an Apprentice",
  "summary": "In a zero-gravity stormtrooper training bay aboard the Star Destroyer Inquisitor, the Sith Warlord Vassily Korolov drills against battle droids when the pirate captain Arissa Kiiko returns, swallowing her pride to seek his help in pursuit of revenge. Suited into EVA armor, Arissa enters Korolov's weightless domain, where he urges her to unlearn her old habits and become one with the void. When she demands to know his price, Korolov names it plainly: he wants her entirely, her complete being in life and death, in exchange for his power and that of the Galactic Empire. Torn between her Firrerreo blood's horror at slavery and her Echani desire for perfection, Arissa is ultimately driven by her hunger for vengeance to submit, calling him Master. Korolov demands unquestioned loyalty on pain of death and, sensing great latent power in her, sends her to rest and open her mind to her new dark reality, as a strange chant grows louder in her head and both Sith brace to bind their souls together.",
